replies.txt_content:
29.03 11:46:18 [Server] ERROR The trait sentry failed to load for NPC ID: 0
.03 11:46:13 [Server] ERROR Plugin Scoreboards v1.0.2 has failed to register events for class io.github.sjj118.scoreboards.CreditChangeListener because io/github/sjj118/credit/CreditChangeEvent does not exist.
29.03 11:46:13 [Server] ERROR Plugin Scoreboards v1.0.2 has failed to register events for class io.github.sjj118.scoreboards.GroupChangeListener because io/github/sjj118/vip/GroupChangeEvent does not exist.
意思分别是：
1 给编号是0的NPC加载交易失败
2 无法给计分板注册点券修改的时间
3 无法给计分板注册VIP修改的时间
